    <string name="readme_text">Project 5: Android Phone Bill App\n\nThis app creates a phone bill for a customer, adds phone calls, pretty prints phone bills, and searches for calls between two times.\n\nRequired input formats:\n- Phone number: nnn-nnn-nnnn\n- Date/time: MM/dd/yyyy h:mm a\n  Example: 03/11/2026 9:15 PM\n\nData persistence:\nPhone bill data is saved to Android internal storage and survives app restarts.\n\nAuthor: Jay Abegglen</string>
